events.description: The Australian stock index climbed 1.6% to 8,847 on Monday, rebounding from previous losses.
Significant gains in US stocks last Friday influenced the Australian market opening.
A busy week of corporate earnings reports in Australia.
CAR Group reported higher H1 net profit and reaffirmed its FY26 outlook.
